ßIN LOVING MEMORY OF BART MOORE-GILBERT, 1952-2015
Beloved father, lovely husband, dear friend, fabulous writer
We miss you so much, but you live on in our hearts
Love always, your 'sniggle' family, Anna, Maddy and Luke xxx"ņ
ķLaughter, sunshine, first football kick with Daddy, and love
bigger thank this park. Let these ingredients of childhood
happiness always stay with you. For our boys, Yuli and Ilya
grandparents, Galina and Valery Vasiliev. May 2011"Ņ
ļGood night sweet Prince and may
flights of angels sing you to your rest.
Thank you for being my friend.
JD

Neil Young
11th April 1961 - 15th July 2019
You were our sunshine
Ali, Izzie, Charlotte, Family & Friends
Forever in our hearts"­
ĒIn Loving Memory of
Michael & Bridget Gannon
Forever in our Hearts
Moisan Family
xxxxxx

Those you love don't go away.
They walk beside you every day.
Unseen, unheard, but always near.
Still loved, still missed, still very dear."¾
